# Smooth Dielectric BSDF

## Algorithm

![](images/smoothBSDF.png width=\pagewidth)

$$L_s(x,\omega) = F L_i(\omega_{mirroeed}) + (1-F)\frac{\eta_i^2}{\eta_o^2} L_i(\omega_{refracted})$$

## result

![](images/table_path.png width=\pagewidth)

# Rough Dielectric BSDF

## Microfacet Models for Refraction through Rough Surfaces [Walter et al. 2009]

![Micro vs. macro surface](images/roughBSDF1.png width=\pagewidth)

![Shadowing-masking geometry](images/roughBSDF2.png width=\pagewidth)

![Half vector](images/roughBSDF3.png width=\pagewidth) 

$$f_s(i,o,m) = \frac{F(i,h_r)G(i,o,h_r)D(h_r)}{4|i\cdot n||o\cdot n|} + 
\frac{|i\cdot h_t||o\cdot h_t|}{|i\cdot n||o\cdot n|}\frac{\eta_o^2(1-F(i,h_t))G(i,o,h_t)D(h_t)}{(\eta_i(i\cdot h_t)+\eta_o(o\cdot h_t))^2}$$

## result

![](images/cbox_roughglass_compare.png width=\pagewidth)

